{{Otheruses|Shrines named "Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine" or "Wakamiya Hachiman-sha"|General description of Wakamiya Hachiman shrines|Wakamiya Hachiman-gū}}'''Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine''' (若宮八幡神社, Wakamiya Hachiman Jinja) or '''Wakamiya Hachiman-sha''' (若宮八幡社, Wakamiya Hachiman-sha) are {{ill|Shrines|ja|神社|qq=draft}} found throughout {{ill|Japan|ja|日本|qq=draft}}.

