* {{ill|Kagurazaka Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine|ja|神楽坂若宮八幡神社|qq=draft}} – [[Tokyo]], [[Shinjuku Ward]], [[Wakamiyachō (Shinjuku)|Wakamiyachō]]
