* {{ill|Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine (Bungotakada, Ōita)|ja|若宮八幡神社 (豊後高田市)|qq=draft}} – [[Ōita Prefecture]], [[Bungotakada, Ōita|Bungotakada]], Takada
* {{ill|Hiji Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine|ja|日出若宮八幡神社|qq=draft}} – Ōita Prefecture, [[Hiji, Ōita|Hiji Town]], [[Hayami District, Ōita|Hayami District]]

